name: objName
description: IAU name for this object.

name: objAltName1
description: Alternate name for this object.

name: objAltName2
description: Altername name for this object.

name: objAltName3
description: Altername name for this object.

name: objID
description: Unique object identifier.

name: uniquePspsOBid
description: Unique internal PSPS object identifier.

name: ippObjID
description: IPP internal object identifier.

name: surveyID
description: Survey identifier.  Details in the Survey table.

name: htmID
description: Hierarchical triangular mesh (Szalay 2007) index.

name: zoneID
description: Local zone index, found by dividing the sky into bands of declination 1/2 arcminute in height: zoneID = floor((90 + declination)/0.0083333).

name: tessID
description: Tessellation identifier.  Details in the TessellationType table.

name: projectionID
description: Projection cell identifier.

name: skyCellID
description: Skycell region identifier.

name: randomID
description: Random value drawn from the interval between zero and one.

name: batchID
description: Internal database batch identifier.

name: dvoRegionID
description: Internal DVO region identifier.

name: processingVersion
description: Data release version.

name: objInfoFlag
description: Information flag bitmask indicating details of the photometry.  Values listed in ObjectInfoFlags.

name: qualityFlag
description: Subset of objInfoFlag denoting whether this object is real or a likely false positive.  Values listed in ObjectQualityFlags.

name: raStack
description: Right ascension from stack detections, weighted mean value across filters, in equinox J2000.  See StackObjectThin for stack epoch information.

name: decStack
description: Declination from stack detections, weighted mean value across filters, in equinox J2000.  See StackObjectThin for stack epoch information.

name: raStackErr
description: Right ascension standard deviation from stack detections.

name: decStackErr
description: Declination standard deviation from stack detections.

name: raMean
description: Right ascension from single epoch detections (weighted mean) in equinox J2000 at the mean epoch given by epochMean.

name: decMean
description: Declination from single epoch detections (weighted mean) in equinox J2000 at the mean epoch given by epochMean.

name: raMeanErr
description: Right ascension standard deviation from single epoch detections.

name: decMeanErr
description: Declination standard deviation from single epoch detections.

name: epochMean
description: Modified Julian Date of the mean epoch corresponding to raMean, decMean (equinox J2000).

name: posMeanChisq
description: Reduced chi squared value of mean position.

name: cx
description: Cartesian x on a unit sphere.

name: cy
description: Cartesian y on a unit sphere.

name: cz
description: Cartesian z on a unit sphere.

name: lambda
description: Ecliptic longitude.

name: beta
description: Ecliptic latitude.

name: l
description: Galactic longitude.

name: b
description: Galactic latitude.

name: nStackObjectRows
description: Number of independent StackObjectThin rows associated with this object.

name: nStackDetections
description: Number of stack detections.

name: nDetections
description: Number of single epoch detections in all filters.

name: ng
description: Number of single epoch detections in g filter.

name: nr
description: Number of single epoch detections in r filter.

name: ni
description: Number of single epoch detections in i filter.

name: nz
description: Number of single epoch detections in z filter.

name: ny
description: Number of single epoch detections in y filter.
